blockhost-broker (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Rust implementation
  * On-chain authentication via NFT contract ownership
  * Lazy polling for request processing (no unbounded loops)
  * Silent rejections (requests expire naturally)
  * ECIES encryption compatible with Python eciespy
  * WireGuard peer management
  * SQLite-based IPAM database

 -- Blockhost <contact@blockhost.io>  Sun, 02 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000
